stories.text:
We are hiring!!

zero5 is looking for a full-stack engineer who has solid experience with React, NodeJS, and Typescript to come in as an early member of our growing team.

Have you ever been late to the meeting because you couldn’t find parking? Or have you ever lost a ticket and had to pay for the whole day's parking? We are changing the entire parking experience by tackling the core problem of the industry - manual process.

With a vision to transform parking spaces into tech-enabled mobility service hubs, we are building automated parking management solutions using the latest software stacks and cloud technologies. You’ll collaborate with a fun and close-knit agile team to architect, implement, test, and continuously deliver new features and products to our customers. If you are interested, we’d love to hear from you!

https://angel.co/recruit/jobs/1704126
